HEADWORD: Mid
<hw>Mid</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Middle.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>About the <qex>mid</qex> of night come to my tent.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mid</ent>⟦br⟧

